{"tid":1017733,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇番以前嘅戲 想講一講張曼玉嘅「靚」","createTime":"2019-02-11T15:56:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-13T07:35:38.000Z","uid":57854,"like":80,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"6bd873343322cbc2e3dc0f8e20f3fa66989bff83","tid":1017733,"uid":57854,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:56:28.000Z","msg":"好多人話張曼玉靚 同時亦有一大堆人話張曼玉唔靚 覺得 王祖賢 鍾楚紅 邱淑貞 關之琳 周慧敏 張敏 朱茵呢堆比佢過至而無不及<br />\n但想講 張曼玉嘅「靚」係靚在「氣質」係可以駕馭一切角色 一切裝扮嘅「氣質」而且個樣（未衰老個樣）好耐看 睇極都唔會厭 唔會睇耐咗而覺得佢俗套 市井 路人樣 <br />\n<br />\n花樣年華嘅旗袍嘅雍容典雅<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KhiPZPx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKhiPZPx.png&h=1cc62f86&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jmOTG2S.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjmOTG2S.png&h=128ed5db&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n濟公做「九世雞」嘅媚態<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gePLx2L.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgePLx2L.png&h=a9addbdc&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ogTPZHM.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FogTPZHM.png&h=bfcd87ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阮玲玉嘅古典<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUayG5c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUayG5c.png&h=f6be6042&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/dbG6hDL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FdbG6hDL.png&h=68a5cdec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n東邪西毒嘅落寞<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zYN1QZO.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzYN1QZO.png&h=efc5ee6c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yJGRtMt.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FyJGRtMt.png&h=7784630c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n青蛇嘅妖艷<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VCKr18h.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVCKr18h.png&h=01c40986&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n同埋以下例子<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HQe34m3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHQe34m3.png&h=48d09ddf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iBxQKm3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiBxQKm3.png&h=8c3bd39b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/VosX8OK.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FVosX8OK.png&h=41388c42&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6CsM18K.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6CsM18K.png&h=53571c3a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4gogEVq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4gogEVq.png&h=d3d1bebb&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nK7X8OL.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnK7X8OL.png&h=93d07235&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C13o4m6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC13o4m6.png&h=e019c207&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n以前會覺得 朱茵（逃學威龍、西遊記時期係癲峰）係最靚 但慢慢地都會覺得略嫌唔夠氣質 然後先發覺張曼玉嘅「靚」係脫俗得嚟帶點平凡 四隻字「花樣年華」<br />\n<br />\n唔好拎近照出嚟 嚇親人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24332a4054fae4be5265dd7598f3a37915563a59","tid":1017733,"uid":232594,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:58:45.000Z","msg":"花樣年華入面佢真係好有氣質<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30776f539d265099b5fa78ac49c6ed1e0f287bb1","tid":1017733,"uid":175896,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-11T15:59:56.000Z","msg":"真人好似好串"},{"pid":"b89ebee64d91cca3e93744ada195a4cb0dfc02b0","tid":1017733,"uid":57854,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"24332a4054fae4be5265dd7598f3a37915563a59","tid":1017733,"uid":232594,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":